# GM_HMS - Hospital Management System Overview

Welcome to the comprehensive overview of **GM_HMS**, a robust, multi-role Hospital Management System built with PHP, MySQL (using both PDO and mysqli), and custom front-end interfaces.

---

## 📂 Codebase Directory Structure

Here is a summary of the core directories and their roles:

- [api/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/api): Central endpoint router. Handles routing all `/api/*` endpoints to the respective controllers.
- [config/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/config): Environment and security settings.
  - [.env](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/config/.env): Key-value environment parameters (e.g. database credentials, mail settings, JWT settings).
  - [SecurityConfig.php](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/config/SecurityConfig.php): Config singleton parsing the `.env` settings.
- [controler/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/controler): Business logic.
  - [BaseController.php](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/controler/BaseController.php): Base class implementing request validation, authorization checks, rate limiting, and HTTP response helpers.
  - [api/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/controler/api): 35+ specialized API controllers handling auth, admin actions, doctors, patients, billing, laboratory, pharmacy, and vendor portals.
- [core/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/core): System-level classes:
  - [Autoloader.php](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/core/Autoloader.php): PSR-4 compatible custom class loader mapping namespaces (like `Controllers\`, `Models\`, `Database\`, etc.) to directories.
  - [Router.php](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/core/Router.php): Dispatcher parsing request paths against regex routes.
- [Database/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/Database): Secure database layers:
  - [SecureDatabase.php](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/Database/SecureDatabase.php): Core `mysqli` singleton query wrapper with automated parameter binding and type detection.
  - [AuditLogger.php](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/Database/AuditLogger.php): Logger recording system activities and security events.
- [models/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/models): DB schema entities (19 files total) managing appointments, billing, prescriptions, laboratory service rates, inventory, staff, and vitals.
- **Views (Role-Based)**:
  - [view/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/view): Admin dashboard, management screens (departments, doctors, staff, laboratory).
  - [doctors_view/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/doctors_view): Consultations, prescriptions (with generic-brand mapping), IPD/OPD patient lists, and symptom analysis.
  - [reception_view/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/reception_view): Registration, booking, billing, and doctor availability.
  - [nurse_view/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/nurse_view), [pharmacy_view/](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/pharmacy_view): Role-specific views. (For deep details of the pharmacy workflow, see [pharmacy_system_details.md](file:///C:/Users/sidde/.gemini/antigravity-ide/brain/30129437-3250-4774-9cd0-c50a8291f3d2/pharmacy_system_details.md)).

