## 🌐 API Endpoint Routing Summary

The system is highly structured, routing clean API links to their respective controller classes. Examples from [api/index.php](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/GM_HMS/api/index.php):

| Method | Endpoint Pattern | Controller | Method |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **POST** | `/api/auth/login` | `AuthController` | `login` |
| **GET** | `/api/patients` | `PatientController` | `index` |
| **GET** | `/api/appointments` | `AppointmentController` | `index` |
| **POST** | `/api/opd/vitals` | `OpdController` | `saveVitals` |
| **GET** | `/api/reception/dashboard/summary` | `ReceptionController` | `getDashboardSummary` |

